  "title": "Kindergarten Teacher - English #76875",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Education (Montessori)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Kindergarten Teacher - English</strong></li><li>Working Location: East</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday to Friday: 8:00AM - 5:00PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $3800 + AWS + Medical and Insurance</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Engage children with a lively and passionate teaching style.</li><li>Foster a dynamic classroom environment conducive to learning.</li><li>Plan and deliver vibrant, suitable lessons.</li><li>Compile developmental reports and maintain individual portfolios for each child annually.</li><li>Exhibit excellent verbal and written communication abilities.</li><li>Keep a positive outlook and a commitment to ongoing personal and professional development.</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties assigned by Superior.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>ECDA Certification –L2</li><li>Applicants currently completing their Diploma in Early Childhood Education will also be considered.</li><li>At least 1 year of experience in a similar role required.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76875 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
